{"tid":1729496,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"反送中運動中的物理(1)----催淚彈融馬路","createTime":"2019-11-17T08:55:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T13:20:29.000Z","uid":325563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"18b4218d417b56ae7086ad10b5a4299b519225cd","tid":1729496,"uid":325563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T08:55:15.000Z","msg":"班黑警射嘅催淚彈究竟可以有幾熱?<br />\n<br />\n我有個朋友係讀物理嘅，佢寫左份研究，估算十一月二日粒融左馬路嘅催淚彈有幾熱，而家有答案啦<br />\n堆數好複雜，如果唔想睇D步驟可以直接跳去結論。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rxLY5Wx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrxLY5Wx.jpg&h=6f8e9aef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OGkus9S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOGkus9S.jpg&h=109deaac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TansZgy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTansZgy.jpg&h=3bf40836&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZX93xBy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZX93xBy.jpg&h=6de6041c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o75qLWz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo75qLWz.jpg&h=e9feee9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tBdoxBz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtBdoxBz.jpg&h=bbbefa5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n總結: 粒催淚彈 <strong>起碼</strong> 有550 度，比一般催淚彈高二百度以上。高溫亦會令CS分解做氰化氫(俗稱山埃)，增加吸入催淚煙後對身體嘅負面影響。如果不幸射中手足，更可能導致嚴重燒傷，後果不堪設想。<br />\n希望大家可以細心睇下份報告，有咩問題可以提出，我會轉達翻比我個朋友知。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>查警暴，止警謊<br />\n光復香港，時代革命</strong>"},{"pid":"72e28b612b34cf57bea7e1f05eac7af592513c73","tid":1729496,"uid":313341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T09:03:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"44f3d82d8249c041e23f902922e21d10080ade6a","tid":1729496,"uid":26836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T11:00:14.0